Hope's torturous innings is ended, just when he might have been getting settled.

commentary: Root to Hetmyer, OUT there's the breakthrough! Joe Root was brought on for this express purpose, and he plucks the return catch as Hetmyer miscues a simple drive down the ground. The partnership comes to an end 11 short of getting to three figures!

commentary: Holder to Stokes, FOUR runs fuller ball, and he has whipped this through midwicket to seal the win. Root and Stokes give each other a hug, as they should. This has been an overall professional performance from the hosts, and that has certainly lifted the gloom from all the washouts over the last week or so at this World Cup!
